&lt;p&gt;# Comments: 7&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=48765450</guid><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jul 2026 18:23:03 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Ask HN: Will AI force CS to focus on what to build instead of how to build it?</title><link>https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=48765447</link><description>&lt;p&gt;As AI becomes really good at the implementation part, it seems that what's left for humans to focus on is what to build.&lt;p&gt;Do you think this will be the case and CS will change accordingly in its focus?&lt;/p&gt;
